Chelsea travel to Valencia on Match Day 5 of the Champions League on Wednesday. The Blues lost 1-0 to the LaLiga side in their first Group H fixture. All the top three teams in the group are on seven points, with two matches left. Kick off is 9pm West African time. Wednesday, November 27
